<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Karina's Clean Living | Home Cleaning & Organizing — Crockett, CA</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --sand: #e8e0d4;
      --linen: #f4f0ea;
      --warm-white: #faf8f5;
      --stone: #b5a899;
      --bark: #7a6a5a;
      --earth: #5c4a38;
      --charcoal: #2c2622;
      --sage: #8a9e82;
      --sage-light: #c4cebf;
      --cream: #f0ebe3;
      --text: #3a3028;
      --text-light: #7a6e64;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background-color: var(--warm-white);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NAVIGATION ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.4rem 4rem;
      background: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(181,168,153,0.2);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--earth);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.8rem;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--bark);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--earth); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 8rem 2rem 5rem;
      background-color: var(--charcoal);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?w=1600&q=80');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      opacity: 0.22;
    }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(44,38,34,0.6) 0%, rgba(44,38,34,0.4) 60%, rgba(44,38,34,0.8) 100%);
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--sage-light);
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.3s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.0;
      color: var(--warm-white);
      margin-bottom: 0.15em;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.6s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--sand);
    }
    .hero-rule {
      width: 60px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--stone);
      margin: 2rem auto;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.85s forwards;
    }
    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--sand);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s 1s forwards;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s 1.2s forwards;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      padding: 1rem 2.8rem;
      background: var(--earth);
      color: var(--warm-white);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--bark); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-secondary {
      padding: 1rem 2.8rem;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--sand);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(232,224,212,0.45);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(232,224,212,0.08);
      border-color: var(--sand);
    }
    .scroll-hint {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2.5rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s 1.8s forwards;
    }
    .scroll-hint span {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--stone);
    }
    .scroll-line {
      width: 1px; height: 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--stone), transparent);
      animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes scrollPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
      50% { opacity: 1; }
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
    section { position: relative; }
    .section-inner {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2.5rem;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--sage);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .section-body {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--text-light);
      max-width: 580px;
    }
    .thin-rule {
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--stone);
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    /* ── ABOUT ── */
    #about {
      padding: 9rem 0;
      background: var(--warm-white);
    }
    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 7rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .about-image-block {
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-image-main {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      background: var(--sand);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .about-image-main img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }
    .about-image-accent {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -2.5rem;
      right: -2.5rem;
      width: 55%;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      background: var(--cream);
      border: 8px solid var(--warm-white);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .about-image-accent img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }
    .about-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--sand);
      margin-top: 3.5rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--sand);
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      padding: 1.6rem 1.4rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--earth);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    /* ── SERVICES ── */
    #services {
      padding: 9rem 0;
      background: var(--linen);
    }
    .services-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }
    .services-header .thin-rule { margin: 1.5rem auto; }
    .services-header .section-body { margin: 0 auto; }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--sand);
      border: 1px solid var(--sand);
    }
    .service-card {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      padding: 2.8rem 2.2rem;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .service-card:hover { background: var(--cream); }
    .service-icon {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
      display: block;
    }
    .service-name {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }
    .service-desc {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }
    .service-price {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--bark);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone);
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }

    /* ── PHILOSOPHY ── */
    #philosophy {
      padding: 9rem 0;
      background: var(--charcoal);
    }
    .philosophy-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .philosophy-quote {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--sand);
      border-left: 2px solid var(--bark);
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }
    .philosophy-text p {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.95;
      color: rgba(244,240,234,0.65);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .pillars {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .pillar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .pillar-dot {
      width: 5px; height: 5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--sage);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .pillar-text {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(244,240,234,0.75);
    }
    #philosophy .section-label { color: var(--sage); }
    #philosophy .section-title { color: var(--sand); }

    /* ── TESTIMONIALS ── */
    #testimonials {
      padding: 9rem 0;
      background: var(--warm-white);
    }
    .testimonials-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4.5rem; }
    .testimonials-header .thin-rule { margin: 1.5rem auto; }
    .testimonials-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      background: var(--linen);
      border-top: 2px solid var(--sage-light);
    }
    .testimonial-stars {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--bark);
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .testimonial-text {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .testimonial-author {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    /* ── CONTACT ── */
    #contact {
      padding: 9rem 0;
      background: var(--linen);
    }
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .contact-details {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .contact-item-icon {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .contact-item-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }
    .contact-item-text strong {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--bark);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .contact-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }
    .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .form-label {
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--bark);
    }
    .form-input, .form-textarea {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--sand);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .form-input:focus, .form-textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--bark);
    }
    .form-textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
    .form-input::placeholder, .form-textarea::placeholder {
      color: var(--stone);
    }
    .contact-form .btn-primary { margin-top: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; border: none; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      background: var(--charcoal);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(181,168,153,0.15);
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--sand);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .footer-tagline {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--stone);
    }
    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: rgba(181,168,153,0.45);
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 1.2rem 1.8rem; }
      .nav-links { gap: 1.5rem; }
      .about-grid, .philosophy-inner, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3.5rem; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-image-accent { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.2rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVIGATION -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Karina's Clean Living</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="#philosophy">Philosophy</a></li>
      <li><a href="#testimonials">Reviews</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Crockett, California &nbsp;·&nbsp; Est. 2008</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Professional<br><em>Home Organizer</em><br>& Housekeeper</h1>
      <div class="hero-rule"></div>
      <p class="hero-tagline">Abundance Grows Where Energy Flows</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Request a Cleaning</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn-secondary">View Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-hint">
      <span>Scroll</span>
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section id="about">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-image-block">
          <div class="about-image-main">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800&q=80" alt="Organized home" />
          </div>
          <div class="about-image-accent">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556909114-f6e7ad7d3136?w=400&q=80" alt="Clean kitchen" />
          </div>
          <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">~20</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Years of Service</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">★★★★★</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Yelp Rated</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Woman Owned</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">1:1</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Same Cleaner, Always</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="section-label">About Karina</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">A Trusted Presence<br>In Your Home</h2>
          <div class="thin-rule"></div>
          <p class="section-body">
            Karina has been bringing clarity, calm, and deep-clean excellence to homes across the East Bay for nearly twenty years. What sets her apart isn't just her meticulous attention to detail — it's the trust she builds with every single client.
          </p>
          <br>
          <p class="section-body">
            When you book with Karina's Clean Living, you get <em>Karina</em>. The same reliable, skilled, English-speaking professional comes to your home each visit — no strangers, no surprises, no shortcuts.
          </p>
          <br>
          <p class="section-body">
            Chemical-free and eco-conscious options are available, and Karina is happy to use the products you prefer. Your home, your standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="services-header">
        <p class="section-label">What Karina Offers</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
        <div class="thin-rule"></div>
        <p class="section-body">From routine refreshes to deep resets, every service is tailored to your home and your life.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
