        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-icon">✨</span>
          <h3 class="service-name">Deep Cleaning</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">A thorough, top-to-bottom cleanse of your home. Ideal for seasonal resets, move-ins, or any time you want your space to feel genuinely renewed.</p>
          <span class="service-price">By quote</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-icon">🏡</span>
          <h3 class="service-name">Professional Home Organizing</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">More than cleaning — Karina helps you reclaim your space. Decluttering, organizing, and creating systems so your home supports the life you want to live.</p>
          <span class="service-price">3 hrs · $200 and up</span>
        </div>
