          <span class="service-price">3 hrs · $400 and up</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-icon">🌱</span>
          <h3 class="service-name">Eco-Friendly Cleaning</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">Chemical-free and natural product options available for families, pets, and those with sensitivities. Clean living, in every sense of the word.</p>
          <span class="service-price">Available on request</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-icon">🔮</span>
          <h3 class="service-name">Home Organizing & Energy Clearing</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">If you have areas overwhelmed with stagnant clutter and stuck energy, Karina combines deep physical cleaning with intentional space-clearing so your home doesn't just look clean — it <em>feels</em> clean.</p>
          <span class="service-price">By quote</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section id="philosophy">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="philosophy-inner">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label">Karina's Philosophy</p>
          <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--sand);">Experienced &<br><em>Creative</em> Home Care</h2>
          <div class="thin-rule" style="background:var(--bark);"></div>
          <p class="philosophy-quote">
            Abundance grows where energy flows — and energy flows best in a clean, clear, cared-for space.
          </p>
        </div>
